<paragraph base="F18632144" id="IFRS01_23A"><paranum>23A</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="23A"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS01_P0103">An entity that has applied IFRSs in a previous period, as described in <xref base="F18657258" href="IFRS01_4A.dita#IFRS01_4A" id="IFRS01_X0181">paragraph 4A</xref>, shall disclose:</p><ol base="F18632146" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS01_L0011"><li id="IFRS01_23A_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F18632147" id="IFRS01_P0104">the reason it stopped applying IFRSs; and</p>       </li><li id="IFRS01_23A_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F18632149" id="IFRS01_P0105">the reason it is resuming the application of IFRSs.</p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>